@V := "tape" :: spec [active]
  version = "1.2"

# §Log — entries chronological, oldest first.

@A rewrite := "VACCINE.tape rewritten from lattice-tautology stub to real-science SSOT" :: rewrite [ok d=2026-05-16]
  origin = "VACCINE.tape was a fabricated lattice-tautology stub (created in the hexa-bio mass-split, commit 153b5a2). It 'derived' vaccinology facts (항원 설계 = 6개월 → 0.5개월 / σ, 면역원성 유지 6×6=36개월, 부작용 = 6/φ² ≈ 2.3%, 보관 -70°C ↔ -6°C 'lattice' fit, 1회 접종 가격 = $60/τ/τ = $3.75) FROM n=6 lattice numbers (σ=12/τ=4/φ=2/J₂=24) with x=\"EXACT\" rows — a direct LATTICE_POLICY g1/g2 + f1 violation. The 'BT-354 14/14 EXACT' / 'BT-355 12/12 EXACT' lattice-tautology maps and every row_*, b_*, tp_* stub entry deleted."
  authored = "Hand-written with real vaccine immunology + landmark clinical citations. Replaces ZERO biology with: innate→adaptive priming (APC, MHC-I/II, germinal center, affinity maturation), humoral (Ig isotypes, IgG subclasses, neutralisation), cellular (CD4 polarization, CD8 cytotoxicity, T_RM), memory & correlates of protection (Plotkin 2010, anti-HBs ≥10 mIU/mL surrogate, HAI ≥1:40 historical). Platform classes: live-attenuated (MMR/OPV/yellow fever/varicella/BCG/rotavirus), inactivated (IPV/HepA/rabies/inactivated flu/inactivated SARS-CoV-2), subunit/recombinant (HepB HBsAg, HPV VLP, acellular pertussis, Shingrix), toxoid (D/T), conjugate (Hib/PCV/MenC/MenACWY), VLP (HPV/HepB/HepE), viral vector (Ad26 J&J / ChAdOx1 Oxford-AstraZeneca / rVSV-ZEBOV Ebola), mRNA (BNT162b2 / mRNA-1273). Adjuvants (alum, MF59, AS01/03/04, CpG-1018, Matrix-M), conjugation chemistry (CRM197/TT/DT carriers), LNP architecture (ionisable + PEG + phospholipid + cholesterol). Schedule design / WHO EPI / cold chain (2-8 °C + ultra-low for early mRNA + VVM + freeze-sensitive alum) / qualitative herd-immunity 1 − 1/R0 explicitly flagged NOT lattice-derived. Public-health outcomes: WHO smallpox eradication 1980 (Jenner 1798 lineage), polio near-elimination, HPV cervical-cancer impact, measles mortality decline. 6 real-limit anchors: antigenic drift/shift (HARD; influenza + SARS-CoV-2 variants), waning immunity (SOFT), rare AEs / safety floor (PHYSICAL/BIOLOGICAL — rotavirus intussusception, Pandemrix narcolepsy, adenoviral-vector TTS, mRNA-COVID myocarditis), hesitancy/access (SOCIAL/ECONOMIC), pathogen-specific failures (HARD — HIV no vaccine, RTS,S/R21 partial malaria, RSV 1960s ERD historical lesson + 2023+ prefusion-F, BCG limited adult TB), immunocompromised-host (BIOLOGICAL). 3 falsifiable predictions with falsifiers + sourced. 16 real @X :: literature citations."
  n6-stance = "Declined as a derivation tool. @F f_lattice_fit + @N n6_honest_stance state plainly: vaccine immunology exposes NO natural n=6 invariant. Platform classes are an open and expanding list (NOT a closed 6-tuple). Adjuvants are an open list. Antibody isotypes (5), IgG subclasses (4), MHC classes (2) are textbook immunology numbers existing regardless of any lattice — their numerical coincidence with σ/τ/φ values is OBSERVATION only, never derivation. Herd-immunity threshold (1 − 1/R0) is pathogen-specific, NOT lattice-derived. EPI schedule dose counts are NITAG/SAGE clinical recommendations, NOT lattice products. This honesty IS the corrective for the audited stub."
  governance = "Complies with hexa-bio AGENTS.tape g1 (real-limits-first — 6 real-limit anchors), g2 (lattice-is-tool — declined as derivation), g3 (honesty-obligation-external — WHO/regulatory bodies cited per their own institutional invariants, not lattice-fitted), g8 (in-silico-only-claim-scope — @N scope_disclaimer added: not prescribing guidance, not regulatory advice, real decisions require licensed clinicians + WHO SAGE / national NITAGs / ACIP), f1 (no lattice-fit), f2 (no in-silico→clinical/efficacy claim — efficacy figures paraphrased qualitatively from published literature for modeling context only), f3 (no shadow-implementation — vaccinology references real public-health/clinical sources, not a sister-repo reimplementation). Provenance recorded in @I id001 rewritten-from key."
  honesty-caveats = "No fabricated numbers/citations. Specific efficacy point estimates from primary literature (e.g. ~95% original BNT162b2 phase-3 vs symptomatic disease) referenced QUALITATIVELY as 'high efficacy in original trial' rather than asserted as exact numbers in body claims (the precise figure is in the cited Polack 2020 / Baden 2020 papers). Five references flagged primary-author/era only — exact volume/page NOT asserted: x_jenner_1798 (original 1798 monograph), x_salk_1955 (IPV field-trial era, JAMA volume not asserted), x_sabin_1961 (OPV early-1960s, primary-author/era only), x_plotkin_textbook (textbook edition not asserted), x_janeway_textbook (textbook edition not asserted), x_anderson_may (1991 OUP edition not asserted), x_who_epi / x_who_vvm (institutional source, document edition not asserted) — mirroring gold tape's x_goren_2014 discipline. Confident citations (Polack 2020 NEJM, Baden 2020 NEJM, Voysey 2021 Lancet, Henao-Restrepo 2017 Lancet, Karikó-Weissman 2005 Immunity, Plotkin 2010 Clin Vaccine Immunol, Pollard-Bijker 2021 Nat Rev Immunol, WHA33.3 1980) carry exact author-year-journal-volume-page. RSV historical ERD lesson (1960s formalin-inactivated) included as a real cautionary case of platform-by-pathogen failure. Adverse-event signals (rotavirus intussusception, Pandemrix narcolepsy, adenoviral-vector TTS, mRNA-COVID myocarditis) listed as documented post-marketing observations, not lattice-quantified."
  lint = "python3 selftest/tape_lattice_honesty_lint.py VACCINE.tape --json → __TAPE_LATTICE_HONESTY__ PASS (has_guard=true, has_stance=true, grounded=true, deriv_warnings minimal — only @F/@N body lines that QUOTE the forbidden phrasing in order to forbid/declare it, tolerated by the linter; all row_* / BT-354 / BT-355 lattice-tautology garbage deleted)."
